OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784296099
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted murder of
OL,4,Cformer partner
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for 20 years
OL,7,Fafter attempting to kill his then
OL,8,Fpartner in Kewstoke, Weston-super-Mare.
OL,10,FJames Stock was convicted of the
OL,11,Fattempted murder of Caroline Goddard,
OL,12,Fafter repeatedly trying to strangle
OL,13,Fher during an assault which lasted 45
OL,14,Fminutes in total.
OL,16,FAvon and Somerset Police officers
OL,17,Fresponded to a 999 call from Ms
OL,18,FGoddard on the 27 July 2025, during
OL,19,Fwhich she reported that Stock was
OL,20,Ftrying to kill her.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
