PN,40402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784296100
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted murder of
OL,4,Cformer partner
OL,6,FOfficers found Caroline unresponsive
OL,7,Fon the ground and with multiple
OL,8,Finjuries, including a bruised and
OL,9,Fswollen right eye, a fractured nose
OL,10,Fand swelling to her neck.
OL,12,FDC Olivia Steward, an officer in the
OL,13,Fcase, praised Ms Goddard, saying:
OL,14,F"Caroline has agreed to share her
OL,15,Fstory to give other victims and
OL,16,Fsurvivors of domestic abuse the
OL,17,Fconfidence to report and speak out
OL,18,Fabout what has happened.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1784296100
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted murder of
OL,4,Cformer partner
OL,6,F"She has showed incredible courage
OL,7,Ffrom the moment the attack began by
OL,8,Fphoning for help, and she's supported
OL,9,Four investigation throughout to
OL,10,Fachieve this outcome."
OL,12,FStock, a 40-year-old from Clevedon,
OL,13,Fpleaded guilty to intentional
OL,14,Fstrangulation, but denied the
OL,15,Fattempted murder charge.
OL,17,FHe was sentenced for his crimes on 15
OL,18,FJuly.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
